Package vooga.towerdefense.action.actionlist

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CreateElement
    Creates a new game element and confers upon it an affiliation code that identifies it with its creator.
    FollowPath
    Makes the action initiator follow a path.
    LevelTimerAction
    A simple Action that disables itself after a certain amount of time.
    ModifyPlayerAttribute
    Modifies the player attribute value by applying another attribute value to it.
    PaintAttributes
    This is a test paint attribute action.
    PeriodicAction
    Defines an action that executes periodically.
    PlayerStatAction
    Action for changing player's score/life/money or any other stat that Player has in a game If the Player class was changed, this needs to be changed.
    RandomChance
    Performs followup actions based on a random chance
    RemoveGameElement
    Removes a game element from the game map.
    SoundAction
    An action that plays a sound whenever executed
